      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve treated it with so much love\u2014always garage-kept and pampered. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! You won't find a single flaw on this beauty; it\u2019s truly in pristine, tip-top shape. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
