    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "An exceptional E46 M3, this specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing, operating with surgical precision. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity, ensuring neutral handling and high-speed stability. The exterior boasts original paint with flawless clear-coat depth, and the cabin is a time capsule of Nappa leather and intact trim. This is a mechanically transparent, concours-ready driver's car.",
