      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a garage-kept 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in pristine condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained, appearing exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating and a strictly hand-wash-only regimen; there are zero stone chips, scratches, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is completely free from sun exposure or tactile wear. Every switch and button operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, featuring a documented service history from authorized dealerships and a clean bill of health. This is a rare, collector-grade example for the driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
